		{
			dependencies: ["542CDE05F61489C1"]
			description: [
				"Like so many quests, this one starts with cobblestone. You're going to need a lot of it."
				""
				"To automate this, you'll need help from our friend, the &aMantis Shrimp&r. Tame him with &9tropical fish&r, tell him to break blocks, and then hand him the block to break with shift+right click!"
				""
				"Keep in mind that he can only breathe in the water. If you lose him, you can buy more from a pet store in a village."
			]
