		{
			dependencies: ["542CDE05F61489C1"]
			description: [
				"Animals seem complex, but when you get down to it, they're mostly just wads of fur and meat. If we hope to reconstruct the king of all animals, we're going to need to gather a lot of that sort of thing."
				""
				"&9Fur balls&r may not sound appealing, but you will be surprised at their uses. The first ingredient, of course, is &9fur&r. Most mammals have it, including &aRaccoons&r, &aGazelle&r, and &aBison&r. You will need to find some of these animals, capture them, and then breed them for their &9fur&r."
				""
				"And hey, if you get some good meat to eat in the process, all the better!"
			]
			id: "4A08737D7BD6DA01"
			rewards: [
				{
					id: "241DCBCE5E58DF3B"
					item: {
