		{
			dependencies: ["4A08737D7BD6DA01"]
			description: [
				"You've probably sheared &aSheep&r for &9wool&r before, but these sheep are a little different. They come with varied genetics. Some are have genes which produce a lot of &9wool&r, some produce only &9leather&r. You would do well to breed the fluffier ones for maximum &9wool&r production."
				""
				"As an alternative, you may be able to find wooly &aLlamas&r instead, or even particularly fluffy &aRabbits&r. Any of these are viable for a wool farm."
				""
				"Keep in mind: none of the above animals are hermaphroditic. They have males and females now!"
			]
